name: House Tarbeck
summary: House Tarbeck of Tarbeck Hall was an ancient house from Tarbeck Hall near the Crag in the Westerlands. They were quite influential until they rebelled with House Reyne against their Lannister overlords. The rebellion was broken by Tywin Lannister. In the course of putting down the rebellion the house was exterminated. According to semi-canon sources they blazoned their arms with a seven-pointed star, parts silver parts blue, on silver and blue field.[1]
